comments: During Thompson's (CLE) dribble, he makes contact with the ball with both hands and then continues dribbling.
Bertans (WAS) and Thompson (CLE) engage with each other during the rebound and after Thompson makes contact with the ball, the two players release.
Sexton (CLE) makes incidental contact to the arm of Bertans (WAS) after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Bryant (WAS) and Sexton (CLE) make incidental contact with each other attempting to get to the loose ball.
Garland (CLE) makes contact to the arm of Bryant (WAS) that affects his play at the basket.
Thompson (CLE) cleanly blocks Bryant's (WAS) shot attempt at the rim.
Bertans (WAS) commits a take foul on Osman (CLE).
Sexton (CLE) and Bryant (WAS) engage with each other following the pick, but Sexton does not dislodge him from his obtained position.
Thompson (CLE) jumps alongside of Beal's (WAS) path to the basket and legally contests his shot attempt at the rim.  Beal creates the marginal contact by extending his off-arm.
Bryant (WAS) makes contact to the arm of Sexton (CLE) that affects his ability to secure the rebound.
Bryant (WAS) firms up in a screening position in Garland's (CLE) path and does not deliver contact.
Nance Jr. (CLE) makes marginal contact to the body of Bryant (WAS) during his putback shot attempt.
Bryant (WAS) has his off-arm placed on Thompson's (CLE) back but the contact is marginal and he does not affect his trajectory during the shot attempt at the rim.
Nance Jr. (CLE) and Thompson (CLE) make incidental contact with Beal (WAS) as all three players jump for the rebound.
Bryant (WAS) commits a take foul on Sexton (CLE).
